Package: vobsub2srt
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: tesseract-ocr-all
Description: Converts VobSub subtitles (.idx/.srt format) into .srt subtitles.
 VobSub2SRT is a simple command line program to convert .idx / .sub subtitles
 into .srt text subtitles by using OCR. It is based on code from the MPlayer
 project - a really great movie player.
 Tesseract is used as OCR software.
